text: Went recently with my friends to celebrate Highlight's 25th birthday!! The party was super fun, we had a tea demonstration and watched an exclusive performance piece (the artist was there too!!!!!). Food was superb. 10/10, highly enjoyed myself, would come again :)
A wonderful brand new gallery with art which makes us think. Located within the beautifully restored premises of the historic Goh Loo Club, this is a must visit when in Singapore.
An exceptional gallery in Singapore with a well-curated collection of art. A must visit for any art collector or enthusiast.
Singapore's top art space, a beautiful gallery
